@startuml
title UC02 Credential owner が利用権を委譲する

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore

Owner -> UI: grant 管理画面を開く
UI -> Firestore: owner の credential 一覧を取得
Firestore --> UI: credential 一覧
UI --> Owner: 委譲対象の credential を表示

Owner -> UI: credential を選択
Owner -> UI: 委譲先を入力\n(個人メールアドレスまたはメールドメイン)
UI -> API: grant 作成を要求
API -> Firestore: grant を保存
Firestore --> API: 保存完了
API --> UI: grant 作成成功
UI --> Owner: 委譲完了を表示
@enduml
